{"tid":699884,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"世界盃會引致跌市係咪真？","createTime":"2018-06-13T01:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T07:33:47.000Z","uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d69ce6554798702f6ca5ad589dde712ecb4afd06","tid":699884,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求解<br />\n<br />\n全球已踏入2018年，今年體育界將舉行一項盛事，就是俄羅斯主辦足球世界盃決賽周。不過，這往往成為金融市場「魔咒」。 <br />\n<br />\n始創「世盃後美股跌市魔咒」的倫敦宏觀經濟預測諮詢公司Lombard Street research首席歐元區經濟學家Dario Perkins曾警告，金融市場動盪與世盃舉行時間不謀而合，例如1930年首屆世界盃，美國處於經濟大蕭條、1990年又遇上美國經濟衰退、1994年債市大屠殺、1998年亞洲金融風暴、2006年美國樓市泡沫爆破、2010年歐債危機、2014年俄羅斯經濟崩潰，環球經濟增長放緩。<br />\n<br />\nPerkins警告，自二次大戰後，美國GDP平均擴張期不超過5年，現時已是金融海嘯後經濟擴張期的第8年。根據往績，2018年下半年，即世界盃後，金融市場恐怕難有運行。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180101/mobile/bkn-20180101155021453-0101_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180101%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180101155021453-0101_00842_001.html&d=jLxFJ%2FU7YEb3387IAD0s0whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f3e57029\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180101/mobile/bkn-20180101155021453-0101_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"93182197dbd9dfe07503efde072f13b8efe95683","tid":699884,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba73f17e2bdd555a2444c57cab5d45097b19e2fc","tid":699884,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你信？<br />\n2012開始年年都有樓價會跌的消息。"},{"pid":"ef524747d07574affc5ce955c508fb230189f2cf","tid":699884,"uid":161374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"咁多年世界盃中得7次都仲要問"},{"pid":"340fdfb6c8aa4a915c548a6f1a2e0ea5f0564788","tid":699884,"uid":150400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:33:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}